{"tid":1019825,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人中/大學真係排斥/欺凌過人？","createTime":"2019-02-13T07:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T08:40:10.000Z","uid":68813,"like":8,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9a073668404f5b06d0b0e6690d48d5c4a4f402cc","tid":1019825,"uid":68813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T07:53:00.000Z","msg":"個日聽朋友講佢試過玩個無朋友既男仔，<br />\n係school picnic時燒一隻跌落地下既雞翼請佢食，仲有好多其他野。<br />\n<br />\n個下先知原來都幾多人係會欺凌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f985b94406c9bafe10db81c2be40e1a045a6fb0c","tid":1019825,"uid":125460,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:12:34.000Z","msg":"你的朋友就是....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3641b9b23d41c70397bd85ca8e962e18e3a468e6","tid":1019825,"uid":236558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:13:46.000Z","msg":"其實大把...出來職埸都見唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4939c7cd37172879167b3700aa240a12bef80fea","tid":1019825,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"@埋大Tim少"},{"pid":"1bba5a182f3854d7f953b336c73871913977eaf0","tid":1019825,"uid":178682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3883097bc1aee59911ead83ffee27449e358d8b","tid":1019825,"uid":66128,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:26:31.000Z","msg":"呢d欺凌人地既人真係死全家都唔夠。<br />\n<br />\n最好身患絕症但係長命百歲。"},{"pid":"016dc82e30cc089489b76b7b68c57b86c5eed76a","tid":1019825,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3641b9b23d41c70397bd85ca8e962e18e3a468e6","tid":1019825,"uid":236558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:13:46.000Z","msg":"其實大把...出來職埸都見唔少<img sr